---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Nous rejoindre" description="Rejoignez l'Étoile Cycliste Ouvrière de Firminy - Conditions d'adhésion et inscription">
  <div class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Rejoignez l'ECOF
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Découvrez comment faire partie de notre communauté de cyclistes passionnés
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Pourquoi nous rejoindre -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Pourquoi rejoindre l'ECOF ?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Communauté bienveillante</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Rejoignez une communauté de cyclistes passionnés et bienveillants, prêts à partager leur expérience et leurs conseils.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-green-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Encadrement professionnel</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Bénéficiez d'un encadrement professionnel avec des moniteurs diplômés pour progresser en toute sécurité.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Parcours exceptionnels</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Découvrez les plus beaux parcours de la Loire et de la région Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes avec des sorties variées.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Formules d'adhésion -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Nos formules d'adhésion</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Formule Découverte -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-200">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Découverte</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">45€</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">2 sorties par mois</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Prêt de vélo inclus</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Assurance incluse</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-400">Entraînements</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-8 bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir cette formule
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Formule Passion -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-blue-500 relative">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <span class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Populaire</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Passion</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">75€</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Sorties illimitées</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Prêt de vélo inclus</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Assurance incluse</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Entraînements inclus</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-8 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir cette formule
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Formule Compétition -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-200">
            <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Compétition</h3>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">120€</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600">par an</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Tout inclus</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Coaching personnalisé</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Participation compétitions</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Matériel haut de gamme</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full mt-8 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Choisir cette formule
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Processus d'inscription -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Comment s'inscrire ?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contactez-nous</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Appelez-nous ou envoyez un email pour manifester votre intérêt</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sortie d'essai</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Participez à une sortie gratuite pour découvrir le club</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dossier d'inscription</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complétez votre dossier avec les pièces justificatives</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bienvenue !</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Vous êtes membre, participez à votre première sortie officielle</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Prêt à nous rejoindre ?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          N'hésitez pas à nous contacter pour plus d'informations ou pour planifier votre sortie d'essai gratuite.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="mailto:contact@ecof-fontainebleau.fr" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Nous contacter par email
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+33123456789" class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold border border-blue-600 transition-colors">
            Appeler le club
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>